ul and a feeling that can be loosely expressed in words as "I am done here.=
 I have nothing more left to do. Time to leave" filled my entire consciousn=
ss.<BR><BR>I had experienced the same kind of intense energy twice before t=
hat. Once I experienced the same energy when I was meditating sitting next =
