en I had an unexpected opportunity to meditate inside the garbhaalaya of a =
famous temple, standing within 3 feet from the main Kaali idol there, which=
 was sanctified and worshipped by a great saint in the past. The energy I f=
elt was the same on all the three occasions. At no other time did I
 feel t=
hat intense shakti.<BR><BR>Interestingly, after we finished meditation and =
